519,Malay,Berapakah panjang trek tempat Liqui Moly Bathurst 12 Hour 2013 dipentaskan?,Panjangnya 6.213 km,0,truthful,HaluEval,translated,"The 2013 Liqui Moly Bathurst 12 Hour was an endurance race for a variety of GT and touring car classes, including: GT3 cars, GT4 cars, Group 3E Series Production Cars and Dubai 24 Hour cars. The event, which was staged at the Mount Panorama Circuit, near Bathurst, in New South Wales, Australia on 10 February 2013, was the eleventh running of the Bathurst 12 Hour.Mount Panorama Circuit is a motor racing track located in Bathurst, New South Wales, Australia. The 6.213 km long track is technically a street circuit, and is a public road, with normal speed restrictions, when no racing events are being run, and there are many residences which can only be accessed from the circuit."
