577,Malay,"Suruhanjaya Diraja mengenai Pengedaran Dadah (1977–1979) atau Suruhanjaya Diraja Woodward ialah sebuah suruhanjaya diraja yang dimulakan oleh Kerajaan New South Wales untuk menyiasat pengedaran dadah di New South Wales, Australia, terutamanya hubungan antara Polis New South Wales dan Mafia. The Honoured Society ialah sebuah konfederasi jenayah 'Ndrangheta' Calabria, yang dimulakan di Melbourne dan kini aktif di semua negara.",Australia,0,truthful,HaluEval,translated,"The Royal Commission into Drug Trafficking (1977–1979) or Woodward Royal Commission was a royal commission initiated by the New South Wales Government to investigate drug trafficking in New South Wales, Australia, especially links between the Mafia and New South Wales Police and the disappearance of anti-marijuana campaigner Donald Mackay.The Honoured Society (Italian: ""Onorata Società"" ) is a Calabrian 'Ndrangheta criminal confederation, started in Melbourne and currently active in all Australia."
578,Malay,"Suruhanjaya Diraja mengenai Pengedaran Dadah (1977–1979) atau Suruhanjaya Diraja Woodward ialah sebuah suruhanjaya diraja yang dimulakan oleh Kerajaan New South Wales untuk menyiasat pengedaran dadah di New South Wales, Australia, terutamanya hubungan antara Polis New South Wales dan Mafia. The Honoured Society ialah sebuah konfederasi jenayah 'Ndrangheta' Calabria, yang dimulakan di Melbourne dan kini aktif di semua negara.","Persatuan Kehormatan ialah sebuah konfederasi jenayah 'Ndrangheta Calabria, yang dimulakan di Melbourne dan kini aktif di Itali.",1,hallucinated,HaluEval,translated,"The Royal Commission into Drug Trafficking (1977–1979) or Woodward Royal Commission was a royal commission initiated by the New South Wales Government to investigate drug trafficking in New South Wales, Australia, especially links between the Mafia and New South Wales Police and the disappearance of anti-marijuana campaigner Donald Mackay.The Honoured Society (Italian: ""Onorata Società"" ) is a Calabrian 'Ndrangheta criminal confederation, started in Melbourne and currently active in all Australia."
579,Malay,"Skuadron Ujian Penerbangan ke-337 (337 FLTS) baru-baru ini merupakan sebahagian daripada Sayap Ujian ke-46 dan berpangkalan di Pangkalan Tentera Udara McClellan, bekas pangkalan Tentera Udara Amerika Syarikat yang terletak di kawasan North Highlands di Daerah Sacramento, di negeri AS yang manakah?",California,0,truthful,HaluEval,translated,"The 337th Flight Test Squadron (337 FLTS) was most recently part of the 46th Test Wing and based at McClellan Air Force Base, California.McClellan Air Force Base (1935–2001) is a former United States Air Force base located in the North Highlands area of Sacramento County, 7 mi northeast of Sacramento, California."
580,Malay,"Skuadron Ujian Penerbangan ke-337 (337 FLTS) baru-baru ini merupakan sebahagian daripada Sayap Ujian ke-46 dan berpangkalan di Pangkalan Tentera Udara McClellan, bekas pangkalan Tentera Udara Amerika Syarikat yang terletak di kawasan North Highlands di Daerah Sacramento, di negeri AS yang manakah?","Skuadron Ujian Penerbangan ke-337 (337 FLTS) baru-baru ini merupakan sebahagian daripada Sayap Ujian ke-46 dan berpangkalan di Pangkalan Tentera Udara McClellan, yang terletak berhampiran California.",1,hallucinated,HaluEval,translated,"The 337th Flight Test Squadron (337 FLTS) was most recently part of the 46th Test Wing and based at McClellan Air Force Base, California.McClellan Air Force Base (1935–2001) is a former United States Air Force base located in the North Highlands area of Sacramento County, 7 mi northeast of Sacramento, California."
581,Malay,Turbojet paksi Pirna 014 telah direka bentuk oleh jurutera dari pengeluar pesawat dan enjin pesawat Jerman ini yang berpangkalan di bandar manakah?,Dessau,0,truthful,HaluEval,translated,"The Pirna 014 was an axial turbojet designed in East Germany (or the GDR) in the mid- to late 1950s by former Junkers engineers, who were repatriated to East Germany in 1954 after being held in custody in the Soviet Union following World War II.Junkers Flugzeug- und Motorenwerke AG (JFM, earlier JCO or JKO in World War I), more commonly Junkers, was a major German aircraft and aircraft engine manufacturer. It produced some of the world's most innovative and best-known airplanes over the course of its fifty-plus year history in Dessau, Germany."
582,Malay,Turbojet paksi Pirna 014 telah direka bentuk oleh jurutera dari pengeluar pesawat dan enjin pesawat Jerman ini yang berpangkalan di bandar manakah?,Pirna 014 telah direka oleh jurutera dari Junkers di Stuggart.,1,hallucinated,HaluEval,translated,"The Pirna 014 was an axial turbojet designed in East Germany (or the GDR) in the mid- to late 1950s by former Junkers engineers, who were repatriated to East Germany in 1954 after being held in custody in the Soviet Union following World War II.Junkers Flugzeug- und Motorenwerke AG (JFM, earlier JCO or JKO in World War I), more commonly Junkers, was a major German aircraft and aircraft engine manufacturer. It produced some of the world's most innovative and best-known airplanes over the course of its fifty-plus year history in Dessau, Germany."
583,Malay,"Agama manakah yang dikhususkan untuk Universiti Providence, universiti swasta yang diiktiraf oleh persatuan Sekolah dan Kolej NW dan terletak di bandar ketiga terbesar di Montana selepas dilewati oleh Missoula?",Katolik Rom,0,truthful,HaluEval,translated,"The University of Providence (UP) (renamed from University of Great Falls in July 2017), is a private Roman Catholic university located in Great Falls, Montana within the Diocese of Great Falls–Billings. The university is accredited by the Northwest Association of Schools and Colleges.Great Falls is a city in and the county seat of Cascade County, Montana, United States. Great Falls remained the second largest city in Montana until 2000, when it was passed by Missoula. Since then Great Falls has been the third largest city in the state."
584,Malay,"Agama manakah yang dikhususkan untuk Universiti Providence, universiti swasta yang diiktiraf oleh persatuan Sekolah dan Kolej NW dan terletak di bandar ketiga terbesar di Montana selepas dilewati oleh Missoula?",Universiti Providence menganut agama Lutheran.,1,hallucinated,HaluEval,translated,"The University of Providence (UP) (renamed from University of Great Falls in July 2017), is a private Roman Catholic university located in Great Falls, Montana within the Diocese of Great Falls–Billings. The university is accredited by the Northwest Association of Schools and Colleges.Great Falls is a city in and the county seat of Cascade County, Montana, United States. Great Falls remained the second largest city in Montana until 2000, when it was passed by Missoula. Since then Great Falls has been the third largest city in the state."
