616,Malay,"Roger Avary (lahir 23 Ogos 1965) ialah penerbit filem dan televisyen Kanada, penulis skrip dan pengarah dalam industri media massa Amerika, beliau menulis skrip untuk Beowulf, sebuah filem fantasi epik tangkapan gerakan 3D British-Amerika 2007, yang diarahkan oleh siapa?",Neil Gaiman mengarah Beowulf.,1,hallucinated,HaluEval,translated," He wrote the screenplays for ""Silent Hill"" and ""Beowulf"".Beowulf is a 2007 British-American 3D motion capture epic fantasy film directed by Robert Zemeckis and written by Neil Gaiman and Roger Avary, based on the Old English epic poem of the same name."
617,Malay,"Filem komedi Pra-Kod Amerika yang menampilkan seorang pelakon, penari dan penyanyi Amerika, yang terkenal dengan persembahan dalam filem dan filem muzikal RKO, telah ditayangkan pada tahun berapa?",1932,0,truthful,HaluEval,translated,"Hat Check Girl is a 1932 American Pre-Code comedy film directed by Sidney Lanfield and written by Barry Conners and Philip Klein. The film stars Sally Eilers, Ben Lyon, Ginger Rogers and Monroe Owsley.Ginger Rogers (born Virginia Katherine McMath; July 16, 1911 – April 25, 1995) was an American actress, dancer, and singer, widely known for performing in films and RKO's musical films, partnered with Fred Astaire."
618,Malay,"Filem komedi Pra-Kod Amerika yang menampilkan seorang pelakon, penari dan penyanyi Amerika, yang terkenal dengan persembahan dalam filem dan filem muzikal RKO, telah ditayangkan pada tahun berapa?",Filem itu ditayangkan pada tahun 1938.,1,hallucinated,HaluEval,translated,"Hat Check Girl is a 1932 American Pre-Code comedy film directed by Sidney Lanfield and written by Barry Conners and Philip Klein. The film stars Sally Eilers, Ben Lyon, Ginger Rogers and Monroe Owsley.Ginger Rogers (born Virginia Katherine McMath; July 16, 1911 – April 25, 1995) was an American actress, dancer, and singer, widely known for performing in films and RKO's musical films, partnered with Fred Astaire."
619,Malay,"Versi suntingan ""Just the Two of Us"" mencapai nombor dua di ""Billboard"" Hot 100 di sebalik lagu yang ditulis dan digubah oleh Donna Weiss dan Jackie DeShannon yang menghabiskan berapa minggu di No. 1 di ""Billboard"" hot 100?",sembilan,0,truthful,HaluEval,translated,"""Just the Two of Us"" is a 1981 R&B single written by Bill Withers, William Salter and Ralph MacDonald, which was recorded by Grover Washington Jr. and Bill Withers. An edited version reached number two on the ""Billboard"" Hot 100, staying there for 3 weeks, behind ""Morning Train (9 to 5)"" by Sheena Easton and ""Bette Davis Eyes"" by Kim Carnes.""Bette Davis Eyes"" is a song written and composed by Donna Weiss and Jackie DeShannon, and made popular by American singer Kim Carnes. DeShannon recorded it in 1974; Carnes's 1981 version spent nine weeks at No. 1 on the ""Billboard"" Hot 100 and was ""Billboard""' s biggest hit of 1981."
620,Malay,"Versi suntingan ""Just the Two of Us"" mencapai nombor dua di ""Billboard"" Hot 100 di sebalik lagu yang ditulis dan digubah oleh Donna Weiss dan Jackie DeShannon yang menghabiskan berapa minggu di No. 1 di ""Billboard"" hot 100?","Lagu yang tidak disertai oleh ""Just the Two of Us"" telah menduduki tempat pertama dalam ""Billboard"" Hot 100 selama sepuluh minggu.",1,hallucinated,HaluEval,translated,"""Just the Two of Us"" is a 1981 R&B single written by Bill Withers, William Salter and Ralph MacDonald, which was recorded by Grover Washington Jr. and Bill Withers. An edited version reached number two on the ""Billboard"" Hot 100, staying there for 3 weeks, behind ""Morning Train (9 to 5)"" by Sheena Easton and ""Bette Davis Eyes"" by Kim Carnes.""Bette Davis Eyes"" is a song written and composed by Donna Weiss and Jackie DeShannon, and made popular by American singer Kim Carnes. DeShannon recorded it in 1974; Carnes's 1981 version spent nine weeks at No. 1 on the ""Billboard"" Hot 100 and was ""Billboard""' s biggest hit of 1981."
621,Malay,"Kumpulan muzik manakah yang mempunyai lebih ramai ahli, Saint Motel atau Curve?",Motel Saint,0,truthful,HaluEval,translated,"Saint Motel is an American indie pop band from Los Angeles, whose music has been described as everything from ""dream pop"" to ""indie prog"". The band consists of A/J Jackson (lead vocals, guitar, piano), Aaron Sharp (lead guitar), Dak Lerdamornpong (bass), and Greg Erwin (drums). The band consisted of Toni Halliday (vocals, occasionally guitar) and Dean Garcia (bass, guitar, drums, programming)."
622,Malay,"Kumpulan muzik manakah yang mempunyai lebih ramai ahli, Saint Motel atau Curve?",Curve tiada lagi ahli.,1,hallucinated,HaluEval,translated,"Saint Motel is an American indie pop band from Los Angeles, whose music has been described as everything from ""dream pop"" to ""indie prog"". The band consists of A/J Jackson (lead vocals, guitar, piano), Aaron Sharp (lead guitar), Dak Lerdamornpong (bass), and Greg Erwin (drums). The band consisted of Toni Halliday (vocals, occasionally guitar) and Dean Garcia (bass, guitar, drums, programming)."
623,Malay,"""Funnybot"" ialah episod kedua musim kelima belas siri televisyen animasi Amerika yang dicipta oleh Trey Parker dan Matt Stone.",Taman Selatan,0,truthful,HaluEval,translated," ""Funnybot"" premiered in the United States on Comedy Central on May 4, 2011, the first time a ""South Park"" episode has aired in May since season 10's ""Tsst"" in 2006.The tenth season of ""South Park"", an American animated television series created by Trey Parker and Matt Stone, began airing on March 22, 2006."
