631,Malay,Dalam parti politik apakah orang yang secara rasminya membuka Pusat Spa Diraja pada tahun 1972?,Konservatif,0,truthful,HaluEval,translated,"The Royal Spa Centre is a Theatre in Leamington Spa, England. The Centre was officially opened on 15 June 1972 by Anthony Eden, one time MP for Leamington and Warwick and Prime Minister of the UK.Robert Anthony Eden, 1st Earl of Avon, (12 June 1897 – 14 January 1977) was a British Conservative politician who served three periods as Foreign Secretary and then a relatively brief term as Prime Minister of the United Kingdom from 1955 to 1957."
