795,Malay,Pakar psikiatri forensik manakah yang dirujuk mengenai kes-kes nombor termasuk satu untuk pembunuh upahan yang berkaitan dengan keluarga jenayah DeCavalcante?,Park Dietz,0,truthful,HaluEval,translated,"Park Dietz (born 1948) is a forensic psychiatrist who has consulted or testified in many of the highest profile US criminal cases including Joel Rifkin, Arthur Shawcross, Jeffrey Dahmer, The Unabomber, Richard Kuklinski, the Beltway sniper attacks, and Jared Lee Loughner. He was associated with members of the American Mafia, namely the DeCavalcante crime family of Newark, New Jersey, and the Five Families of New York City."
