813,Malay,"Mookychick ialah majalah dan komuniti dalam talian harian bebas dengan lebih 100,000 pembaca sebulan dan lebih 5,000 ahli forum. Kandungannya merangkumi analisis peristiwa sosiopolitik semasa, trend sosial dan budaya, fesyen alternatif, filem, buku, muzik dan seni serta kraf dari perspektif feminis, berbeza dengan penerbitan dan komuniti feminis seperti majalah gaya hidup wanita yang diterbitkan enam kali setahun dan diterbitkan oleh Debbie Stoller dan Laurie Henzel.",Dada,0,truthful,HaluEval,translated," In contrast with feminist publications and communities such as ""Jezebel"", or ""Bust"", ""Mookychick"" explores gender issues from the perspective of the social outsider who feels they have been marginalised by their lifestyle choices.BUST is a women's lifestyle magazine that is published six times a year."
