845,Malay,Sejauh manakah jarak Bebola Masa Tawaran boleh berada dari Waktu Sejagat Terselaras?,0.9 saat.,0,truthful,HaluEval,translated,"Deal Timeball is a Victorian maritime Greenwich Mean Time signal located on the roof of a waterfront four-storey tower in the coastal town of Deal, in Kent, England. Today GMT is considered equivalent to UTC for UK civil purposes (but this is not formalised) and for navigation is considered equivalent to UT1 (the modern form of mean solar time at 0° longitude); these two meanings can differ by up to 0.9 s. Consequently, the term GMT should not be used for precise purposes."
846,Malay,Sejauh manakah jarak Bebola Masa Tawaran boleh berada dari Waktu Sejagat Terselaras?,Bebola Masa Tawaran boleh dimatikan dari Waktu Sejagat Terselaras sehingga 2.5 saat.,1,hallucinated,HaluEval,translated,"Deal Timeball is a Victorian maritime Greenwich Mean Time signal located on the roof of a waterfront four-storey tower in the coastal town of Deal, in Kent, England. Today GMT is considered equivalent to UTC for UK civil purposes (but this is not formalised) and for navigation is considered equivalent to UT1 (the modern form of mean solar time at 0° longitude); these two meanings can differ by up to 0.9 s. Consequently, the term GMT should not be used for precise purposes."
