857,Malay,Sitkom Korea Selatan apakah yang dibintangi oleh penyanyi dan pelakon Korea Selatan yang memulakan kerjaya muziknya pada usia 15 tahun?,Pengeluar,0,truthful,HaluEval,translated,"The Producers (; lit. Producer) is a 2015 South Korean sitcom starring Cha Tae-hyun, Gong Hyo-jin, Kim Soo-hyun, and IU.Lee Ji-eun (Korean: 이지은 ; born May 16, 1993), better known by her stage name IU (Korean: 아이유 ), is a South Korean singer, songwriter and actress. She signed with LOEN Entertainment in 2007 as a trainee and began her music career at the age of 15 with her debut album, ""Lost and Found""."
