861,Malay,Gelatin ialah sebuah kapal udara yang dipandu pada 19 September 1905 oleh seorang juruterbang Amerika perintis dan apa?,tukang kebun,0,truthful,HaluEval,translated,"Gelatine was an airship operated by the United States Army Signal Corps. On the morning of September 19, 1905, the ""Gelatine"", piloted by Lincoln J. Beachey, ascended from the grounds of the Lewis and Clark Centennial Exposition on the shores of Guild's Lake in Portland, Oregon, landing 40 minutes later at the Vancouver Barracks in Vancouver, Washington.Lincoln J. Beachey (March 3, 1887 – March 14, 1915) was a pioneer American aviator and barnstormer."
